<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.5.3">
<l>nammuṭai nāyakaṉē nāṉmaṟai yiṉporuḷē nāviyuḷ naṟkamala nāṉmuka ṉukkorukāl</l>
<l>tammaṉai yāṉavaṉē taraṇi talamuḻutum tārakai yiṉṉulakun taṭavi yataṉpuṟamum</l>
<l>vimmava ḷarntavaṉē vēḻamu mēḻviṭaiyum viraviya vēlaitaṉuḷ veṉṟuva rumavaṉē</l>
<l>yammave ṉakkorukā lāṭuka ceṅkīrai yāyarkaḷ pōrēṟē yāṭuka vāṭukavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our Lord, Meaning of the four Vedas,</l>
<l>You who at one time became the mother of the four-faced one</l>
<l rend="indent">[born upon] the good lotus in [your] navel!</l>
<l>You who, having stroked all the lands of the earth and the world of the stars,</l>
<l rend="indent">grew to expand even outside of that!</l>
<l>He is the one who, at that time that was appointed,</l>
<l rend="indent">came having conquered the elephant and seven bulls!</l>
<l>Hey! Dance one time for me! Battle bull of the cowherds, dance the Ceṅkīrai, please dance!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
